Carmen Phillips https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carmen_Phillips 0 Carmen Phillips (January 9, 1895 – December 9, 1936) was an American actress of the silent era. She appeared in 61 films between 1914 and 1926. She was born in San Francisco, California. Carmen_Phillips ( January_9_,_1895 – December_9_,_1936 ) was an_American_actress of the_silent_era .
